channel.title: Project unknown development team
channel.description:
I am currently looking for a few more people to enter my server coding team. I have only just started the team and i have coded alot of skills before any one started. I found that this way will make up lost time because i have already spent about 5 days on this server.
[b]Recruites left: 5[/b]
[b]LATEST UPDATE: Cooking interface added[/b]
Forums [url=http://www.projectuknown.co.nr]HERE[/url]
Once you reply to this thread i will pm you the forums address and other details you may require.
You will need to post an application on the forums and we will decide if to accept or not.
Here are some of the skills i have added already.
[b]These skills are currently almost finished. Only minor exp changes or tweaks are required.[/b]
